DataList.LocalizeJP: お、私の番…！？任せて任せて！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Leave it to me, leave it to me.

DataList.LocalizeJP: …私？私…！私だー！頑張る頑張るー！
DataList.LocalizeEN: …I? Me…! It's me! I'll do my best, I'll do my best!

DataList.LocalizeJP:
さあ、私のかっこいい姿を……！
のあっ！？ふぅ……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Now, let's see how cool I look...Oh! Damn...

DataList.LocalizeJP:
ここで大活躍を……！
あぁっ！？危ない危ない……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Let's show our success here...ha! ? Dangerous, dangerous.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
ふふっ、ここで必殺技……！
とあぁっ！？びっくりしたー……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Fufu~, here's the special move... oops! I was surprised….

DataList.LocalizeJP:
信号弾、発射！
行っけえぇぇっ！

私だって
力になれるんだから！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Because I can be strong too.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
ピンチの時こそ颯爽と！
私、登場！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Be dashing when you're in a pinch! I appear.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
うわぁ～、先生これくれるの？
えへへっ、ありがとー！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sensei, thank you for giving me this.

DataList.LocalizeJP:
えぇっ！？これ、私に！？
やったー！

おお、全身に漲るこの力……！
え、そういう効果は無い？なんだ、気のせいか……
DataList.LocalizeEN: oh…. This power fills my entire body. …what? Is there no such effect? What, was it just my imagination?

DataList.LocalizeJP:
え、先生からのプレゼント！？
……これで少しは、背が伸びたりするかな？
DataList.LocalizeEN: A gift from Sensei, I wonder if this will make me grow a little taller

DataList.LocalizeJP:
先生先生、今日暇？
もういっそのこと、修行部に泊まっていかない？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sensei, do you have free time today? Why don't you stay the night at the discipline club?

DataList.LocalizeJP:
おぉ、これで私も素敵なレディーに……！
え、それはちょっと違うかも？んん……？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Oh, I think I can become a wonderful lady too... , maybe that's a little different? Why?

DataList.LocalizeJP:
先生が何かと付き合ってくれるの、本当に嬉しいんだよね。
うん、すっごく好き。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'm really happy that Sensei is going out with me I really like it

DataList.LocalizeJP:
大事な相手には、プレゼントをあげるものなんだって！
だから先生には、私の宝物の……この光る石をあげる！
どう、キラキラしてるでしょ！？
DataList.LocalizeEN: I heard that people are supposed to give presents to their loved ones. That's why I give you my treasure, this shiny stone! copper? It's sparkling, isn't it?
